top 10 short-cuts

1. ctrl + alt + t, terminal
2. ctrl + c, codelite
3. super <--, snap
4. ctrl + q, close application window
5. super + d, minimizes all running application windows and show desktop
6. super/alt + tab, switch between running applications

5 codelite shortcuts
//ctrl + c, CodeLite
//alt + m toggles fullscreen
//ctrl + f9, build and run
//ctrl + f11 toggles minimal view

10 magic commandlines
history | grep cache  // search commands that contains 'cache' pattern
file history  //check the info against history file



super + l, lock screen

super + a, show application menu

ctrl + alt + up/down arrow, move between workspaces



